-05-23T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"唔返新工<br />\n搵過份<br />\n咁賤格，返得都唔慌好做"},{"pid":"00aad5db50d35fb96fd2c3ab3faf4caa20d1ffad","tid":674760,"uid":145882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"咁閪既公司 做落都唔方開心 騎牛搵馬啦"},{"pid":"3731fe47b35c15b365aa0f31487693cd90ce5f6f","tid":674760,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"afd5fa33aa6fe5cc24085c07ca2b817dd0ff6de1","tid":674760,"uid":75692,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:50:22.000Z","msg":"簽定合約先resign<br />\n咪做傻仔<br />\n不過如果真係仆街既<br />\n簽定合約都可以即刻唔要你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"咪就係，話簽左約先個 d 都傻既，根本保障唔到"},{"pid":"f9ccf8b46ce60fbd713ba42c2c425fbdbc001a85","tid":674760,"uid":187962,"like":0,"dislike":66,"score":-66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"我都想唔做份新工，但老豆老母等住我養，有真空期真係唔敢博。<br />\n<br />\n份工需要成日返大陸，望就望自己安安全全，無咩頭暈身興。自己本身個底子唔算好strong，每次病差唔多都要睇兩次醫生先會好，但宜家我病都唔會睇醫生，返去傳染俾班pk都好。"},{"pid":"56dee3321441349e1698488a91fd89cd8270d2c6","tid":674760,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肯定唔會簽"},{"pid":"feb24a7e69391b954064e7e27f165c3ffe4d0cf1","tid":674760,"uid":129016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:06:50.000Z","msg":"唔做啦更係"},{"pid":"3f7a1058abb150152206713416b578870390529d","tid":674760,"uid":137627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"錢事少...可以睇得出間公司一定係閪公司，所以一定唔做"},{"pid":"eeb555219c013d35fbab5c8bd5d09eb0d6a102eb","tid":674760,"uid":133533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"賤到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b8043642cde08b85455af6640be73f8c52340a","tid":674760,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f7a1058abb150152206713416b578870390529d","tid":674760,"uid